80
00:03:23,430 --> 00:03:25,390
from threatening the Communist Party—

81
00:03:25,390 --> 00:03:27,530
the Uighur people of Xinjiang.

82
00:03:27,530 --> 00:03:28,530
But don’t worry!

83
00:03:28,530 --> 00:03:31,889
