00:05:28,759 --> 00:05:30,060
In more news about how well

131
00:05:30,060 --> 00:05:33,520
the Chinese Communist Party is regulating
religion,

132
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:36,360
Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesman Geng Shuang

133
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:40,580
