150
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:27,280
Anyway, the current Dalai Lama is getting
on in age—

151
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:30,340
meaning, he might have to reincarnate soon.

152
00:06:30,340 --> 00:06:31,790
But don’t worry,

153
00:06:31,790 --> 00:06:33,720
because the next Chinese Dalai Lama

154
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,650
will endorse the Communist Party.

155
00:06:35,650 --> 00:06:38,050
They’ll make sure of it.

156
00:06:38,050 --> 00:06:40,190
Bad news for the Chinese economy.

157
00:06:40,190 --> 00:06:42,120
Companies are defaulting on their debts

158
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:44,490
at an 'unprecedented' level.

159
00:06:44,490 --> 00:06:46,349
On the show we’ve spoken about how bad

160
