debt within the shadow banking system

161
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:52,289
has created a huge debt bubble in China.

162
00:06:52,289 --> 00:06:55,669
So authorities are doing what they do best:

163
00:06:55,669 --> 00:06:57,030
Cracking down.

164
00:06:57,030 --> 00:06:58,129
The flip side is,

165
00:06:58,129 --> 00:07:00,759
shadow banking is the primary credit provider

166
00:07:00,759 --> 00:07:02,940
for a lot of Chinese companies.

167
00:07:02,940 --> 00:07:07,220
So the crackdown could actually be making
things worse.

168
00:07:07,220 --> 00:07:09,860
You know, maybe the Chinese Communist Party

169
00:07:09,860 --> 00:07:12,970
