170
00:07:12,970 --> 00:07:14,889
Just something for the suggestion box.

171
00:07:14,889 --> 00:07:18,229
I hear the Party is really open to suggestions.

172
00:07:18,229 --> 00:07:19,729
Please don’t purge me.

173
00:07:19,729 --> 00:07:22,699
Foxconn, the company that makes your iPhones,

174
00:07:22,699 --> 00:07:26,220
