not to take China’s Huawei,

199
00:08:26,199 --> 00:08:29,440
but to take this soccer jersey instead.

200
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:32,349
Because the soccer jersey can’t spy on him.

201
00:08:32,349 --> 00:08:33,480
Just to be clear,

202
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,320
Trump did not actually say that.

203
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,360
It was a joke.

204
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,770
I don’t want to be responsible

205
00:08:37,770 --> 00:08:40,360
for the next Gorilla channel.

206
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,360
And finally,

207
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,880
there’s a new trend in China:

208
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:45,080
People are using social media

209
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:47,770
