220
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:14,090
So some people starting posting photos

221
00:09:14,090 --> 00:09:17,560
of themselves in goth makeup on Sina Weibo—

222
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:19,480
the Chinese version of Twitter.

223
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:21,170
And amazingly,

224
00:09:21,170 --> 00:09:24,850
the “Guangzhou Metro has since apologized
on Weibo

225
00:09:24,850 --> 00:09:27,270
for ‘inappropriately’ handling the matter,

226
00:09:27,270 --> 00:09:28,700
and says it has suspended

227
00:09:28,700 --> 00:09:31,590
the security staffer for retraining.”

228
00:09:31,590 --> 00:09:33,160
Which is surprising considering

229
