234
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:48,820
Now I see why the Communist Party

235
00:09:48,820 --> 00:09:52,060
needs to spend so much money on stability
maintenance.

236
00:09:52,060 --> 00:09:55,430
Peppa Pig is a serious threat to social harmony.

237
00:09:55,430 --> 00:09:57,530
And just wait until Chinese people discover

238
00:09:57,530 --> 00:10:00,540
emo music and guyliner.

239
